00:24:48,600 --> 00:24:50,200
Di mana dia bermalam?

481
00:24:52,020 --> 00:24:53,840
Dia pergi ke Persatuan Segalanya.

482
00:24:53,850 --> 00:24:55,079
Dia berjaga sepanjang malam

